Commitments undertaken by Uzbekistan upon joining the WTO entail complete withdrawal of the State from the economy. That is, from 1 January 2013, Uzbekistan is unfit with the aid-of state funds and is not allowed to limit the private enterprises’ operations in any way, isolate the private sector (such as: declaring a holiday season in the private sector, etc.) or command it (such as: demand pro­-bono work from the private sector or enlist its labour force). The State shall not at any time interfere in any way with the enterprises’ man­ages’ decisions on whom to employ and what conditions to allocate to them. Let’s remember the gift of Byta­nsur Satkhozdaevu to the retired 98 leaders of uzbekistani shipyard chaired by - http://www.ukrjet.com.ua/forum/viewtopic.php?f=20&t=34010&st=0&sk=t&sd=a - Ubaydulla, kazabajazova Shakhrixsa Khoshkhumova Alisherja Abdugaffarov to spare 4,000 tonnes of concrete for the foundation of a nursing home in Atraxeohe.
